    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わーー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Waaaah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6928576548,
      "endTime": 24.160227211200002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "わっ！　びっくりした……\n急に悲鳴が上がったけど、何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wah! That scared me…\nSomeone suddenly screamed. What happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.259524703,
      "endTime": 30.559524703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.7563049395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり……。ここにいる人達はみんな\n私達に注目してるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As I thought…. It seems everyone here\nis paying attention to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7563049395,
      "endTime": 37.1063051302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.3229716062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "注目って……有名人なら分かるけど\n私なんか見かけても嬉しくなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Paying attention…? I understand if it were for celebrities but…\nNo one would be happy to see someone like me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3229716062,
      "endTime": 44.825556826500005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "千紗ちゃーん！　こっち向いてー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chaaan! Look over here~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.022337063,
      "endTime": 47.2414753753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
