      "text": "騒ぎが大きくなる前に早く移動しましょう\n千紗のファンが働いているお店に行くのよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s hurry and move before things get out of hand.\nWe’re going to the store your fan works at‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3087998627,
      "endTime": 58.1673712014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.3754665294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
