      "text": "う、うん……。その人は自分がプロデュースしたお店で\n沢山の人に楽しんでもらうのが夢なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah…. Their dream is to have lots of people\nenjoy themselves at the shop he produced…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.3754665294,
      "endTime": 67.6047182002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
