      "text": "実は、私もなんのお店か知らなくて……お店を下見した\nスタッフさんは「行けば分かる」って言ってたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I don’t know what kind of store it is either… The staff\nwho scouted the place said‚ “You’ll know when you go”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8014984367,
      "endTime": 81.5014980552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
